    - target: {fileID: 5785856218639066180, guid: 70d9b7a6cfe4e0f47885d3167e4bb340, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'You pilot the spaceship that starts out in the middle of the screen.
        You must destroy each cargo ship, and it''s break away containers, by shooting
        them into smaller pieces until they disappear. Besides firing, your ship
        can turn, thrust, and warp to a random location.


        Upon destroying
        every cargo container, you advance to the next stage. Boss spaceships occasionally
        appear and fire bullets at your ship and at the cargo containers. You must
        avoid contact with every cargo container, boss, or bullet.


        1 hit
        and... you are dead!'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
